        <title>Books</title>
        <link>//localhost:1313/books/</link>
        <pubDate>Sun, 21 Jan 2018 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
        
        <guid>//localhost:1313/books/</guid>
        <description>&lt;p&gt;Below you may find a list of books that &lt;em&gt;I have read&lt;/em&gt; and, believing that they are worth reading, &lt;em&gt;I recommend&lt;/em&gt; them. I will be updating this list as I read more books that should be added here.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;system-design&#34;&gt;System design
